# Force HTTPS + canonicalize to https://www.verletics.com
# Root (apex) -> www (preserve path)
https://verletics.com/*   https://www.verletics.com/:splat 301!
http://verletics.com/*    https://www.verletics.com/:splat 301!
# Ensure www -> https (covers any http requests to www)
http://www.verletics.com/* https://www.verletics.com/:splat 301!

# Optional: direct root requests without trailing slash
/   https://www.verletics.com/ 301!

# Fallback: catch-all to index for SPA-style routing (if your app needs it)
# Uncomment the next line if you use client-side routing
# /*   /index.html   200
